                     <interp inst="t17910216-8-person118" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a constable. (Produces the property.)</p>
               <p>(Mrs. Dixon deposed to the handkerchiefs.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was coming up this street, and I heard the cry of stop thief! and that gentleman kicked my shoe off; I was crossing the way to my mother, who lives in the court opposite.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17910216-8-verdict49" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910216-8-verdict49" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
